📌 Project Title

QuizNova – Interactive Questions and Quiz Application

❗ Problem Statement

Students and learners often struggle to find a simple and interactive platform to practice questions and test their knowledge. Most existing systems are either too complex, not user-friendly, or require internet-based platforms with distractions. There is a need for a lightweight, easy-to-use quiz application that helps users practice questions and evaluate their performance instantly.

🎯 Objective

The main objective of this project is to develop a simple and interactive quiz application that:

Provides multiple-choice questions (MCQs)
Allows users to attempt quizzes easily
Calculates and displays scores instantly
Improves learning and self-assessment
Offers a clean and user-friendly interface
💡 Proposed Solution

We propose a web-based Quiz Application where:

Users can start a quiz with one click
Questions are displayed one by one
Users select answers from given options
The system evaluates answers automatically
Final score is displayed at the end
⚙️ Features
📝 Multiple Choice Questions (MCQs)
⏱️ Optional timer per question
📊 Instant score calculation
🔄 Restart quiz option
🎨 Simple and responsive UI
🛠️ Technology Stack
Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
Backend (optional): Python Flask / Node.js
Database (optional): JSON / MongoDB / MySQL
🎯 Target Users
School students
College learners
Competitive exam aspirants
Anyone who wants to test knowledge
📈 Expected Outcome

A fully working quiz system that helps users learn, practice, and evaluate their knowledge in an interactive and engaging way.
